title: Nordo in for PA - Thielen a true #1? Michelleti, Leber, and Jonny Athletic Join.
description: We explore a talker of how Adam Thielen will fare as the true No.1 WR without Stefon Diggs opposite him on the field. Pat Michelletti, Ben Leber, and Jonny Athletic amongst our guests!`
